          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1624887972352-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top your <strong>warmed tortillas</strong> with a dollop of <strong>herby mayo </strong>and the<strong> lettuce leaves</strong></p><p>Spoon over the <strong>smoky black beans</strong>, top with the <strong>pineapple salsa</strong> and garnish with the <strong>quick-pickled onion rings</strong> – these are your<strong> smoky black bean, pineapple & red onion tacos</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
